description: Study To Identify Strategies And Programme To Eradicate Poverty And Improve Employment And Equity Restructuring Among Bumiputera Communities In Sabah and Sarawak

subproject.description: Report detailing the profiles of the poor and extreme poor in Sabah and Sarawak. This report will include a quantitative and qualitative analysis of the various dimensions of income and human poverty in Sabah and Sarawak. A report that identifies the gaps between the proposed strategies, programmes and projects against the poverty reduction targets set.  These will form an action plan towards poverty reduction for Sabah and Sarawak
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: SEDC: Poverty Sabah & S'wak
